2.3 DUIM-Geometry Module

transform?

Generic function

Summary

Returns #t if its argument is a transform.

Signature

transform? object => boolean

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

boolean
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-geometry

Module

duim-geometry

Description

Returns #t if object is a transform, otherwise returns #f.

<transform>, page 64
